<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien hehpih, hehpih lien pen,
 Van nawpna leia hungkum;
 Kei mauah tawm takin chengin,
 Ginum na adim Lalpa.
 Isu, Nang lungsietna na hi,
 Lungsietna thieng tawp ngeilo;
 Hukdamna tawh ei hung veh in,
 Nang ngai lunggil ah chengin.

[V2]
 2. Na lungsietna Thagau hun pie'n,
 Lunggil buoite cheng kiengah;
 Lunggil chengah nang cheng inla,
 Na tiem chawlhna chu mu'ng kau.
 Bangkim bawlthei, ei Hukdam in,
 Na lungsiet ei muh sakin;
 Kintaka hung kihei kita,
 Na Ho-In taihsan lodi'n.

[V3]
 3. Na thilsiem thak chu zo inla,
 Buok beklo leh thieng dingin;
 Ka hukdamna kim uh mu'ng kau,
 Bukim kei a Na bawl chu!
 Lopi apat lopi zaw ding,
 Vana ka muh uh tun ma'n,
 Nang chawian a ka khun mauin,
 Maksa, hehpih chawian in!</lyrics>
<title>LOVE DIVINE, ALL LOVE EXCELLING</title>
</song>